

if you are using  ELM or PINE

start elmtag.pl with  -i  option for automatic installation
or read the documentation.

$ elmtag.pl -i



do  

   more README

to read the User Guide and installation notices.


if you have problems to read 'README' file, you can
recompile the manual page by

   nroff -man elmtag.1 > README


